Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:03.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}我有预感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}多彩的未来
