Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:16.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}再一次学会微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}如此多彩的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:23.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}若是纵身一跃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:26.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}无限的相遇
